item.title: CVE-2023-6012|2024-08-02T08:21:17.001Z -- lanaccess -- onsafe%20monitorhm
item.description: An improper input validation vulnerability has been found in Lanaccess ONSAFE MonitorHM affecting version 3.7.0. This vulnerability could lead a remote attacker to exploit the checkbox element and perform remote code execution, compromising the entire infrastructure.
